txt.en: 'If you ask me, Woodhall is the finest town in the Shire.'
'If you fancy a nighttime stroll, the hills near our town simply cannot be beaten!'
'If you're looking to sample the fine beer of Stock, you need to keep heading east.'
'Rollo Boffin, across the way there, is the hobbit to see if you want to talk pipe-weed.'
